init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My mouth was open and my eyes were focused on the mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I thought maybe i should make sure my eyes werent playing tricks on me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I read the number beside my name.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I quickly began to look at the rankings of all the other dads.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I know there are plenty of dads who work just as hard as i do, and they deserve to be #1 too.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I am not perfect, i know that.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Why cant i just enjoy this?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I dont know the answer to any of these questions...

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: but I hope to figure them out someday.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think i am almost ready to sit down and enjoy this cup of coffee.
